-- Nigeria picks Stanbic, Goldman Sachs for $100 mln Diaspora bond sale
-- By Chijioke Ohuocha
-- Tue Apr 15, 2014 11:54AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, April 15 (Reuters) - Nigeria has appointed Stanbic IBTC Bank <IBTC.LG> and Goldman Sachs <GS.N> as advisers for its debut $100 mln Diaspora bond issue, the debt management office said on Tuesday.

